Package: tailsclock
Architecture: all
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, gir1.2-gtk-3.0 | python-gtk2, gir1.2-panelapplet-4.0 | python-gnomeapplet, gnome-icon-theme, gnome-panel, python-tz
Description: Simple clock applet for Gnome (fallback mode)
 This clock applet is extremely simple. The only configurable option is to
 change the timezone of the displayed time. This timezone change is independent
 of the actual operating system configuration.
